00a64956-ed67-4ec5-9b86-95a2a10fde6d.body:
Dear Felicia,
We hope all is going well! We would like to get some inputs from you, about your experience with Casa Mia Casa Tua. 

We are looking at making some changes and your feedback, as a valuable (former) member of the Casa Mia Casa Tua community, is very much welcomed. Additionally, as you have noticed, we have not organized any type of social activity since before the lockdown (the gift baskets do not really count...), and it would be great to have your feedback on this too.

Here is a short survey, it won't take you more than 2-3 mins to fill:  https://forms.gle/E4Z5QjP1Sz3f3RSn8 

Thanks a lot in advance!


Casa Mia Casa Tua
Follow our Instagram account and like our Facebook page for more updates from us!
